- continuing through a long chain...

Following the complete path through all the intermediate relationships:
Andrew → Brenda → Samantha → Cynthia → Kayla → Christine → William → Eugene → Carol → Daniel → Judith → Theresa → Bobby → Christian → David → Vincent → Marie → Elijah → Ethan → Martha → Joan → Jason → Catherine → Juan → Jonathan → Charlotte → Randy → Alexis → Albert → Hannah → Patrick → Donna → Melissa → Evelyn → Raymond → Kathryn → Steven → Emily → Christopher → Lawrence → Aaron → Ann → Christina → Charles → Bruce → Billy → Kathleen → Patricia → Sara → Amanda → Denise → Cheryl → Dennis → Dylan → Grace → Matthew → Alan → Sean → Gary → Ralph → Nancy → Jennifer → Betty → Philip → Gloria → Jack → Sharon → Shirley → Katherine → Austin → Kevin → Sarah → Kenneth → Henry → Jesse → Barbara → George → Helen → Justin → Samuel → Anthony → Virginia → Natalie → Debra → Diane → Brandon → Douglas → Dorothy → Carolyn → Nathan → Doris → Isabella → Zachary → Madison → Sandra → Diana → Roy → Frank → Bryan → Rebecca → Stephen → Gabriel → Joseph → Sophia → Abigail → Anna → Lauren → Megan → Keith → Emma → Angela → Michael → Paul → Pamela → Jessica → Amber → Andrea → Thomas → Jacob → Mason → Ruth → Jerry → Harold → Kimberly → Joshua → Stephanie → Lori → Janet → Danielle → Russell → Julia → Terry → Victoria → Tyler → Benjamin → Marilyn → Brittany → Judy → Bradley → Robert → Janice → Kelly → Walter → Eric → Timothy → Heather → Jeremy → Logan → Julie → Jose → Nicole → Jeffrey → Michelle → Margaret → Willie → Susan → Arthur → Rachel → Adam → Joe → Jordan → Maria → Peter → Scott → Elizabeth → Wayne → Brian → Amy → Linda → Larry → Gerald → Edward → Lisa → Carl → Frances → Ronald → Teresa → Joyce → Ashley → Roger → Beverly → Laura → Richard → Nicholas → Jean → Gregory → Donald → James → Mary → Olivia → Ryan → Karen

This establishes that Andrew is Karen's ancestor.
